title: ReFX.PlastiCZ.VSTi.v1.02
description:
ReFX.PlastiCZ.VSTi.v1.02


reFX presents PlastiCZ, a new VST instrument with a fresh synthesis, which supplies unheard of sounds.

Shrill: PlastiCZ sounds different. With two phase-morph oscillators and AM you can coax completely new sounds from PlastiCZ, which differs completely from other synthesizers.

Colourful: PlastiCZ has a simple and clearly arranged user interface, the individual modules are differently coloured from each other and all parameters are always accessable.

Fresh: Ten insert-effects give that certain extra to the sounds and offers further possibilities for extravagant sounds.
